    {
      "id": "p1-e25",
      "page": 1,
      "text": "We stay four nights at the centrally located 4* Dukes\u2019 Academie Hotel (https://www.dukesacademie.com/) in Bruges. Located under a fifteen minute walk from the market square, facilities at the hotel include a breakfast room and bar. All rooms are en suite and feature television, tea \u0026 coffee making facilities, and an in room safe. A set three course dinner without drinks is included at the Maximiliaan van Oostenrijk Restaurant (located a 100 metres walk from the hotel) on the first evening. The remaining three nights are on a bed and breakfast basis.",
